{"type": "article", "id": 14176, "title": "“音乐猎手”", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-31T06:58:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004300SZD4o1NlRc5WgQfP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自 Installations And Interaction 工作室的一位设计师 Gemma Roper 推出的一个“音乐猎手”，它是一个互联网启用流装置，效果是让用户可以根据节奏选择音乐，当它接收到节奏信号，会自动重音乐库里面选取相应节奏的乐曲开始播放。播放器强调艺术上的随机性，所以不设置播放记录和播放引导，界面中央像是一个节拍器，可以通过向上向下的滑动改变乐曲的节奏。此外，播放器外观设计十分简洁时尚，<a href=\"http://www.gemmaroper.com/RADIO-ACTIVITY\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看更多信息，<a href=\"http://www.gemmaroper.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以看 Gemma Roper 的更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141752DrsTzMJ8WNChfEK6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141753DmedMn7wZcrJTYCk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55867971\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141754gflr2hUPzXJkmap6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141754U8Gfk9jmcRwPz1QK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614175580c2P5HAwUpI3q7T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141755wTF645H3qfZOkUX7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}